variables.comment:
* Service class flag for all data bearers (including

variables.comment:

variables.name: SERVICE_CLASS_DATA_CIRCUIT_SYNC
variables.comment:

variables.name: SERVICE_CLASS_DATA_CIRCUIT_ASYNC
variables.comment:
* Service class flag for the asynchronous bearer service.

variables.name: SERVICE_CLASS_DATA_PACKET_ACCESS
variables.comment:

variables.comment:
